  "detailed_description": "TOON is a First Person Shooter game.<br><br><strong> - PROCEDURAL LEVEL GENERATION - </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736710/extras/066621be22b6019f51c1b0376be7eee0.avif?t=1716492533\" width=683 height=384 /></span><br><br>Each level is procedural with random elements so you will be faced with unique levels each time you play. <br><br>The fast-paced action is spiced up with a beautiful art found throughout the procedural level generation each time you play.<br><br><strong> - PUNCHES -</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736710/extras/e2923ae1a3085360d49cd2a2237125eb.avif?t=1716492533\" width=682 height=384 /></span><br><br>Gameplay<br>The player enter into a procedural generated level and need to clear the entire level from enemies to go to the next level.<br><br><strong>Features and Content</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Levels with different themes and enemies<br></li><li>  All level are procedurally and ramdomly generated to add more randomness to each gameplay ( Every game is different - random levels ).<br></li><li>  Amazing Art ( Old Cartoon Style )<br></li><li>  Black and White Mode ( Old Cartoon Style )</li></ul><br><strong> - BLACK AND WHITE MODE - </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736710/extras/3d0082825704ee36a8cf6f9e0ba4adcd.avif?t=1716492533\" width=682 height=384 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "TOON is a First Person Shooter game.<br><br><strong> - PROCEDURAL LEVEL GENERATION - </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736710/extras/066621be22b6019f51c1b0376be7eee0.avif?t=1716492533\" width=683 height=384 /></span><br><br>Each level is procedural with random elements so you will be faced with unique levels each time you play. <br><br>The fast-paced action is spiced up with a beautiful art found throughout the procedural level generation each time you play.<br><br><strong> - PUNCHES -</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736710/extras/e2923ae1a3085360d49cd2a2237125eb.avif?t=1716492533\" width=682 height=384 /></span><br><br>Gameplay<br>The player enter into a procedural generated level and need to clear the entire level from enemies to go to the next level.<br><br><strong>Features and Content</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Levels with different themes and enemies<br></li><li>  All level are procedurally and ramdomly generated to add more randomness to each gameplay ( Every game is different - random levels ).<br></li><li>  Amazing Art ( Old Cartoon Style )<br></li><li>  Black and White Mode ( Old Cartoon Style )</li></ul><br><strong> - BLACK AND WHITE MODE - </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736710/extras/3d0082825704ee36a8cf6f9e0ba4adcd.avif?t=1716492533\" width=682 height=384 /></span>",
